    <item>
      <title>CalAmp 申请破产以完成债务重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/calamp-files-bankruptcy-to-complete-lender-backed-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CalAmp Corp. 是一家开发用于跟踪车辆和改善公司物流的软件的公司，该公司已申请破产以完成一项减债协议，将业务控制权移交给贷方 Lynrock Lake Master Fund LP。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/calamp-files-bankruptcy-to-complete-lender-backed-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 13:01:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯机器人利用假冒汤姆·克鲁斯传播奥运会虚假信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/russian-bots-use-fake-tom-cruise-for-olympic-disinformation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据微软公司周日发布的调查结果，亲俄罗斯的宣传组织正在利用人工智能进行大规模宣传，暗示即将举行的巴黎奥运会上可能会发生暴力事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/russian-bots-use-fake-tom-cruise-for-olympic-disinformation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 12:53:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 和 AMD 争夺 AI 控制权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/jensen-huang-computex-keynote-nvidia-reveals-new-ai-software-and-services</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nvidia Corp. 和 Advanced Micro Devices Inc. 的高管展示了推动全球人工智能发展繁荣的新一代芯片，这场竞争加剧，可能决定人工智能设计和应用的方向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/jensen-huang-computex-keynote-nvidia-reveals-new-ai-software-and-services</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 10:10:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利电信首席执行官称电网交易让公司有空间进行未来的并购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/telecom-italia-ceo-says-network-deal-frees-firm-for-future-m-a</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利电信公司 (Telecom Italia SpA) 完成具有里程碑意义的价值 220 亿欧元（238 亿美元）的网络出售后，将为新的交易做好准备，此举旨在让该运营商摆脱数十亿欧元的债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/telecom-italia-ceo-says-network-deal-frees-firm-for-future-m-a</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 08:42:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
