      <title>Atos 将评估 Kretinsky 和 ​​Onepoint 提出的新救助方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/atos-to-assess-new-rescue-offers-from-kretinsky-onepoint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Atos SE 收到了两个竞相收购这家负债累累的法国 IT 公司的财团修改后的出价，并将于本周与债权人一起在两个财团之间做出选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/atos-to-assess-new-rescue-offers-from-kretinsky-onepoint</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 06:35:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币网络软件更新引发争议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/bitcoin-debate-heats-up-over-software-revamp-to-add-new-features</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着通过软件升级代码添加新功能的努力不断推进，比特币区块链作为主要支持数字黄金的网络的声誉可能会发生变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/bitcoin-debate-heats-up-over-software-revamp-to-add-new-features</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>会计调查后，Autodesk 首席财务官被董事会撤换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/autodesk-cfo-replaced-after-internal-accounting-investigation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧特克公司 (Autodesk Inc.) 重新任命首席财务官后，该公司股价出现一年多来的最大涨幅，此举旨在解决导致文件提交延迟数周的内部会计调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/autodesk-cfo-replaced-after-internal-accounting-investigation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 21:05:02 GMT</pubDate>
